These nodes are not perfectly equivalent, but it is definitely true that In=
tel is being more aggressive in terms of new technology. Gate-all-around (R=
ibbonFET/Nanosheet) transistor timelines are similar, but the company will =
bring backside power to market a node before TSMC, as well as EUV-NA. That =
does not mean that the Silicon Valley stalwart will win: new technologies b=
ring new risks and sometimes unfavorable economics (note this piece from Se=
